ZH: 这棵树很高。
EN: This tree is very tall.

ZH: 春天，树上长满了嫩绿色的叶子。
EN: In spring, the tree is covered with fresh green leaves.

ZH: 夏天，树荫下最适合休息。
EN: In summer, the shade of the tree is the best place to rest.

ZH: 秋天，黄色的树叶飘落一地。
EN: In autumn, the yellow leaves fall to the ground.

ZH: 冬天，树枝上挂满了冰晶。
EN: In winter, the tree branches are covered with ice crystals.

ZH: 这片树林里充满了鸟儿的歌声。
EN: The forest is filled with the songs of birds.

ZH: 这些树木都是橡树。
EN: These trees are all oak trees.

ZH: 树干上刻着两个心形的符号。
EN: There are two heart-shaped symbols carved on the trunk of the tree.

ZH: 森林里的大树能够吸收大量二氧化碳。
EN: The big trees in the forest are able to absorb a lot of carbon dioxide.

ZH: 他在树下找到了一只迷失的小猫。
EN: He found a lost kitten under the tree.

ZH: 这个地区的树都被砍伐光了。
EN: The trees in this area have all been cut down.

ZH: 树的根深深地扎在土壤中。
EN: The roots of the tree are deeply embedded in the soil.

ZH: 这棵樱花树的花朵开得很美。
EN: The blossoms on this cherry tree are beautiful.

ZH: 河边种了一排柳树。
EN: A row of willow trees is planted by the river.

ZH: 树上结满了甜甜的果实。
EN: The tree is covered with sweet fruits.

ZH: 这座小山丘上有一片茂密的树林。
EN: There is a dense forest on the small hill.

ZH: 孩子们在树荫下玩耍。
EN: The children are playing in the shade of the tree.

ZH: 风吹拂树叶发出悦耳的声音。
EN: The wind rustles through the leaves of the trees, making a pleasant sound.

ZH: 我们在树下野餐。
EN: We are having a picnic under the tree.

ZH: 树木的年轮显示它的岁月长河。
EN: The tree rings of the tree show its long history.
